Tiwa Savage and son, Jamil Superstar Singer and proud mother-of-one, Tiwa Savage has taken to her social media page to share photos of her recent outing with her mum and son, Jamil Balogun. She shared several pictures in her new 2019 custom Mercedes Benz V250 which she bought a few months ago, and which was reportedly worth N70million. She simply captioned the photos: ”Love mine” Source